TI  - The Recoverability Principle: A Civilizational Limit on System Continuation
PY  - 2026
PB  - Figshare (United Kingdom)
T2  - Figshare
DO  - 10.6084/m9.figshare.31876315.v13
UR  - https://doi.org/10.6084/m9.figshare.31876315.v13
